text:

My experiences span automobile sales, car maintenance, real estate, and campus services, and I’ve taken on leadership roles in billboard installation and volunteer services.



Python programming
Microsoft Office
Basic computer maintenance





English
Mandarin
Cantonese




I’m adaptable on-site, skilled in team coordination, and known for integrating ideas and staying composed under pressure.
